{"tid":1650510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(行動Post)[國際戰線] 15/10 NBA迷首聚修頓 籃波人鏈","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:14:00.000Z","uid":87901,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d9361f519915d0c69b37dc055738e410d7e0c8d9","tid":1650510,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"近排NBA發生咩事唔使我講 大家都知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國球迷眾籌派T-Shirt，全美國人屌到支共七彩，我哋除咗笑鳩大陸冇得睇NBA，係時候做番啲野啦！NBA分分鐘跪，我哋唔幫手，陣間跪咗咪要我哋罷睇啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n所以，繼英超大和解後，到香港NBA球迷聚首修頓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：10月15日<br />\n<br />\n時間：19：30-21：30<br />\n<br />\n地點：修頓球場<br />\n<br />\nDress code：不拘，建議NBA波衫或打波裝束<br />\n<br />\n記住，本次行動為純和理非，製作核彈文宣，見到記者記得要多謝美國球迷<br />\n<br />\n文宣同波友幫手啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">籃波撚 15號，修頓見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/13/115740_9602677f3d5125e0f3211dd1bbb06f88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2F115740_9602677f3d5125e0f3211dd1bbb06f88.png&h=743b70a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1e6439c3f33e7a887fc07671255d4c68571ea7d","tid":1650510,"uid":87901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDfxQhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDfxQhA.jpg